IPRC Musanze ni ikigo cya leta gihugura amashuri makuru yashyizweho kugirango gitange uburezi bwa tekiniki n’imyuga, gikora munsi yu Rwanda Polytechnic. IPRC Musanze yubatswe nkimpano yabashinwa ibinyujije muri Ambasade yayo mu Rwanda.<ref>https://agriprofocus.com/organisation/rwanda-polytechnic-iprc-musanze</ref>

IPRC Musanze yatangiye gufata abanyeshuri bwa mbere ku ya 30 Werurwe 2015, icyo gihe yari ikitwa Musanze Polytechnic ikorera mu kigo gishinzwe iterambere ry'abakozi (WDA). Hamwe no gushinga Rwanda Polytechnic muri 2018, izina ricyo kigo ryarahindutse iza kwitwa IPRC Musanze. IPRC Musanze iha abanyeshuri uburezi bwa tekiniki n’imyuga n'amahugurwa yo kuba abanyamwuga mubijyanye n'ubuhinzi, ubwubatsi, amashanyarazi na elegitoroniki, hamwe no gucunga abashyitsi. Binyuze muri gahunda zikigoabanyeshuri bahabwa impamyabumenyi ya A1 n'amasomo magufi.<ref>https://www.iprcmusanze.rp.ac.rw/services-1</ref>
